    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 430533.0,
      "end_time": 433133.0,
      "text": "We have to keep that feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 433133.0,
      "end_time": 435667.0,
      "text": "close to our hearts"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 435667.0,
      "end_time": 439066.0,
      "text": "to keep this work alive"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 439066.0,
      "end_time": 444200.0,
      "text": "we can’t forget that nature exists."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 444200.0,
      "end_time": 446600.0,
      "text": "That’s probably the most important thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 446600.0,
      "end_time": 448967.0,
      "text": "Chaen-san is originally from Kagoshima"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 448967.0,
      "end_time": 451166.0,
      "text": "but the uniqueness of the Tottori Sand Dunes"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 451166.0,
      "end_time": 452600.0,
      "text": "attarcted him to live here"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 452600.0,
      "end_time": 455233.0,
      "text": "to start this museum."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 455233.0,
      "end_time": 461066.0,
      "text": "Nowhere else can this exhibit be recreated."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 461066.0,
      "end_time": 464266.0,
      "text": "I was able to invite many people"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 464266.0,
      "end_time": 468166.0,
      "text": "from around the world and"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 468166.0,
      "end_time": 470400.0,
      "text": "I could create this situation here."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 470400.0,
      "end_time": 473700.0,
      "text": "The Tottori Sand Dunes and this museum"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 473700.0,
      "end_time": 476300.0,
      "text": "is one of the highlights of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 476300.0,
      "end_time": 479700.0,
      "text": "A very big stage in my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 479700.0,
      "end_time": 482467.0,
      "text": "The sand dunes were created 100,000 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 482467.0,
      "end_time": 485800.0,
      "text": "from sand blowing off the sea, accumulating in this spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 485800.0,
      "end_time": 487967.0,
      "text": "It’s been shrinking because barriers to prevent"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 487967.0,
      "end_time": 490867.0,
      "text": "tsunamis have disrupted the currents and sand flow"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 490867.0,
      "end_time": 493133.0,
      "text": "vegetation creeping in."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 493133.0,
      "end_time": 496133.0,
      "text": "The city is trying to reverse it now because …"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 496133.0,
      "end_time": 497600.0,
      "text": "it’s spectacular."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 497600.0,
      "end_time": 500266.0,
      "text": "Unique and a reason to travel to Tottori."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 500266.0,
      "end_time": 505967.0,
      "text": "Just to see a little Sahara in Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 505967.0,
      "end_time": 507667.0,
      "text": "With loads to do and see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 507667.0,
      "end_time": 510400.0,
      "text": "it’s an awesome escape to a natural and beautiful area"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 510400.0,
      "end_time": 512567.0,
      "text": "of Japan."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 512567.0,
      "end_time": 517800.0,
      "text": "Devoid of all vending machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 517799.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520265.99999999994,
      "text": "Next time: the ONLY in JAPAN Question & Answer episode!"
